{"tid":1271312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲未有人明白成王敗寇呢個道理？","createTime":"2019-07-01T06:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T15:12:15.000Z","uid":4014,"like":395,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3a35a35695ffc3154fea25ed9e010d8207b0793a","tid":1271312,"uid":4014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"香港唔係外國 唔可以同黃背心同日而語<br />\n人地歐洲係真正嘅民主國家<br />\n香港人仲係極權統治下生活<br />\n你一日唔取代呢個政府 佢就一日不斷欺壓你<br />\n呢個時勢仲有人期望和理非<br />\n實際上操控左傳媒就點講都得<br />\n班建制賊同狗官深明呢個道理<br />\n無論你靜坐又好 做烈士都好<br />\n你唔取代佢 自己建立民主政府<br />\n佢都可以不斷攻擊你<br />\n相反就可以利用媒體取得民心<br />\n成王敗寇呀"},{"pid":"e655a4be4773616543b665779fdda438470ae0b3","tid":1271312,"uid":4014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0895a4d11aff38221dd75a0c1f4f2641742df164","tid":1271312,"uid":4014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e076951722cbd36101a86636e128d40f65b4fc3b","tid":1271312,"uid":66839,"like":14,"dislike":61,"score":-47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"笑左， 你整爛幾塊玻璃就推翻到個政府"},{"pid":"1136c14518f02c246849faa703380c243dc23ac1","tid":1271312,"uid":66839,"like":7,"dislike":39,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"人地加泰羅尼亞都未得， 就靠你幾個有勇無謀"},{"pid":"d4058d1b8080a4aeb24e80e7bcdf642b8c92ea9d","tid":1271312,"uid":66839,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"做實事應該搵d 有材能既人做領導， 而家一盤散沙， 冇d 計劃"},{"pid":"53843170be494fedf2bd6cb1e3285e4cde84e593","tid":1271312,"uid":270951,"like":6,"dislike":20,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑左， 你整爛幾塊玻璃就推翻到個政府</blockquote><br />\nd傻仔天真到以為撞爆玻璃可以革命？"},{"pid":"289a7e39c35507dede4575a180ca7339ec60aeb5","tid":1271312,"uid":38548,"like":47,"dislike":4,"sco